{"tid":2409072,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登將與G7領袖開會商疫情及中國挑戰","createTime":"2021-02-15T13:11:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T15:49:46.000Z","uid":278587,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f569c46f87d3671ee3492d3ae21e1ce260c1aad2","tid":2409072,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T13:11:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=424124\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D424124&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BsF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=2a712f2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D424124&h=1f92c4b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=424124</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國總統拜登本周五將參與七國集團視像會議，與成員國領袖討論新冠疫情及對華政策等議題。<br />\n<br />\n這次是拜登就任總統後首度參加國際會議，白宮表示，拜登將跟與會領袖討論通過加大投資增強七國集團的集體競爭力，以及更新國際規則，應對中國所帶來的經濟挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n拜登並會透過與全球主要經濟體領袖會晤，共同商討如何應對新冠疫情和重建全球經濟。白宮指，拜登屆時的重點將放在協調疫苗生產和分配上。<br />\n<br />\n今次視像會議由英國首相約翰遜主持，也是去年四月以來七國集團首次會議。"},{"pid":"f5248132d7d6704fc08c209f90363c6539925862","tid":2409072,"uid":375325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T13:12:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94279f5921e6147adabc40293629e75a8041552","tid":2409072,"uid":370061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T13:13:09.000Z","msg":"推廣<del>戰略性忍耐</del><span class=\"red\">綏靖</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f90b9d73feb178422763b85f0368fb164241d6ae","tid":2409072,"uid":155815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T13:15:37.000Z","msg":"一邊把口屌兩句一邊出行政命令搵人民幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f72e8646eb95d29d9d449d4f15812ec043eb657","tid":2409072,"uid":259674,"like":1,